 10 Apr 2024 09:11:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-opposition-parties-projected-retain-majority-legislature-exit-poll-2024-04-10/</guid></item><item><title>拜登在白宫峰会上欢迎“全球伙伴”岸田</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-welcomes-global-partner-japans-kishida-white-house-summit-2024-04-10/</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登和日本首相岸田文雄将在周三的白宫国事访问期间展示强大且不断发展的伙伴关系，重点是联合防务合作，以遏制咄咄逼人的中国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 09:03:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-welcomes-global-partner-japans-kishida-white-house-summit-2024-04-10/</guid></item><item><title>梅赛德斯-奔驰第一季度销量因亚洲供应瓶颈而下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-benz-q1-sales-drop-supply-bottlenecks-asia-2024-04-10/</link><description>德国高端汽车制造商梅赛德斯·奔驰 (Mercedes Benz) 周三表示，受亚洲供应瓶颈及其豪华车型系列转换的影响，第一季度销量下降 6%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 08:33:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-benz-q1-sales-drop-supply-bottlenecks-asia-2024-04-10/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，香港将于四月批准首个现货比特币 ETF</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hong-kong-set-approve-its-first-spot-bitcoin-etfs-april-sources-say-2024-04-10/</link><description>两位知情人士表示，现货比特币交易所交易基金可能于本月在香港推出，首批批准可能会在下周公布。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 08:26:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hong-kong-set-approve-its-first-spot-bitcoin-etfs-april-sources-say-2024-04-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平称无人能阻止与台湾“家人团聚”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-president-xi-meets-former-taiwan-president-ma-beijing-2024-04-10/</link><description>中国国家主席习近平周三对台湾前总统马英九表示，外界的推论无法阻止海峡两岸“家人团聚”，没有不能讨论的​​问题。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 08:16:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-president-xi-meets-former-taiwan-president-ma-beijing-2024-04-10/</guid></item><item><title>解释者：中国在风力涡轮机制造领域的主导地位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-dominance-wind-turbine-manufacturing-2024-04-10/</link><description>欧盟反垄断专员玛格丽特·维斯塔格(Margrethe Vestager)表示，欧盟将调查中国输往欧洲的风力涡轮机供应商收到的补贴。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 07:57:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-dominance-wind-turbine-manufacturing-2024-04-10/</guid></item><item><title>Grifols 将通过出售票据和上海莱士股份为 2025 年到期的债务进行再融资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/grifols-refinance-debt-due-2025-via-sales-notes-shanghai-raas-stake-2024-04-10/</link><description>西班牙制药商 Grifols 周三表示，计划通过新的高级担保票据的收益以及将其在上海莱士的 20% 股份出售给海尔集团来偿还 2025 年的债务。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 07:43:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/grifols-refinance-debt-due-2025-via-sales-notes-shanghai-raas-stake-2024-04-10/</guid></item><item><title>行业机构表示，中国一直在关闭闲置的汽车产能</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-auto-factory-capacity-is-not-growing-fast-industry-group-says-2024-04-10/</link><description>中国汽车工业协会(CAAM)一位高级官员周三表示，2023年中国汽车工厂产能利用率将超过70%，闲置产能正在关闭。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 07:11:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-auto-factory-capacity-is-not-growing-fast-industry-group-says-2024-04-10/</guid></item><item><title>彭博社称字节跳动全年利润增长 60%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/bytedance-full-year-profit-jumps-60-bloomberg-news-says-2024-04-10/</link><description>彭博新闻周三援引知情人士的话报道称，TikTok 母公司字节跳动的利润在 2023 年增长了约 60%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 07:11:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/bytedance-full-year-profit-jumps-60-bloomberg-news-says-2024-04-10/</guid></item><item><title>商会称大多数德国企业认为在中国存在不公平竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/majority-german-firms-feel-unfair-competition-china-commerce-chamber-says-2024-04-10/</link><description>中国德国商会周三进行的一项调查显示，近三分之二的德国企业认为，他们在中国遇到了来自当地企业的不公平竞争，并且在接触当地官员、信息和许可方面处于劣势。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 07:07:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/majority-german-firms-feel-unfair-competition-china-commerce-chamber-says-2024-04-10/</guid></item><item><title>向中国发出工厂产能警告后，耶伦面临关税决定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/after-issuing-factory-capacity-warning-china-yellen-faces-tariff-decisions-2024-04-10/</link><description>美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦在对广州和北京进行为期四天的访问期间，向中国经济领导人发出严厉警告，称他们对清洁能源产品工厂产能的过度投资是不可接受的。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 05:05:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/after-issuing-factory-capacity-warning-china-yellen-faces-tariff-decisions-2024-04-10/</guid></item><item><title>阿里巴巴马云从阴影中走出来，发表鼓舞士气的帖子</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/alibaba-founder-jack-ma-steps-out-shadows-with-long-internal-post-2024-04-10/</link><description>阿里巴巴联合创始人马云向员工写了一份冗长的备忘录，表达了对这家互联网巨头重组工作的支持，这是这位亿万富翁在过去几年远离聚光灯后的罕见举动。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 04:03:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/alibaba-founder-jack-ma-steps-out-shadows-with-long-internal-post-2024-04-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>